premise_source_doc_sentence: John Kiffmeyer  (  born July 11 , 1969  )  , known professionally in music as Al Sobrante , is an American musician , best known as the former drummer for the punk rock band Green Day .
His name of Al Sobrante is a reference to his hometown , El Sobrante .
His work with Green Day resulted in about 961,000 albums sold , which are mostly from the compilation album 1,039 / Smoothed Out Slappy Hours .
